{"tid":1587090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［哲學］撕紙就係對方主動攻擊，自衛必要而合理","createTime":"2019-09-22T09:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T09:43:20.000Z","uid":40478,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e88f78d13ddfea8ab51cb9b786ec9b37e742448d","tid":1587090,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"人之異於禽獸，就因為人有心靈、思想同信念<br />\n心靈同肉體一樣重要，傷害其他人既心靈同傷害對方既肉體一樣有罪<br />\n唔係好耐之前，有個老師比校長鬧到自殺，難道呢個校長無犯到殺人罪嗎？<br />\n同理，廢中廢老撕紙係傷害緊義士既信念，同傷害義士既肉體係同一惡劣既主動攻擊性質，由此可證，義士係受到攻擊下出手自衛係有必要性既；同樣，眾所週知，由於對香港前途憂慮，近排好多年青人自殺，義士有理由真誠相信如果由廢中廢老撕紙，肆意攻擊年輕人既心靈，係可以致死既，面對死亡威脅，義士無論用乜反擊自衛都屬於合理而克制既武力，應當表揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a33cc4a9f76807377e5dd24fb19203b935f8078","tid":1587090,"uid":13343,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"被撕紙係畀人deprive of freedom of speech<br />\n仲要人地起腳踢手足<br />\n<br />\n成日嗌fight for freedom<br />\n但畀人撕紙<br />\n有手足打人<br />\n又話手足唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27688d3106e76ddae3d83137ce5205b2392e51f8","tid":1587090,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fbf77dce4a3f4e5922a81a32fc0769580d6743c","tid":1587090,"uid":48060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:15:41.000Z","msg":"非常好的解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf8bccfafcf7e026bcca158655e21dd0163a6cd","tid":1587090,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83591851c138736b3f1e044c87fc5e09b6a0c1b","tid":1587090,"uid":293539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:17: